## Document Goal

These are interview-quality architecture notes, not project documentation.
Audience: preparing for Senior AI Engineer, GenAI Architect, Principal AI Engineer,
and AI Platform Architect interviews.

Each document must include: executive summary, problem statement, why this approach,
architecture overview, deep dive, design patterns, alternatives comparison,
migration strategy, production considerations, and interview Q&A.
